{"type":"message","id":"d31dde67","parentId":"28def1be","timestamp":"2026-03-18T10:40:00.053Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:5cab973e-d17e-41d2-b5c3-419ba9651915 管管进化心跳 - 每20分钟] 【第 N 轮进化心跳】\n\n执行20分钟进化轮次：\n\n## 第一步：搜索 (3分钟)\n- 使用 web_search 搜索 AI Agent 相关最新信息\n- 搜索 5-10 个不同来源\n\n## 第二步：阅读提取 (5分钟)\n- 使用 web_fetch 读取有价值的内容\n- 提取 1-2 个核心要点\n\n## 第三步：写作产出 (10分钟)\n- 将提取的内容写成笔记，保存到 knowledge/ 对应目录\n- 如果有可复用的框架，提取为模板\n- 如果有实战经验，整理为案例\n\n## 第四步：反思优化 (2分钟)\n- 读取当前的 evolution-plan.md\n- 根据本轮执行情况，思考如何优化方案\n- 更新 evolution-plan.md（优化执行流程、调整时间分配等）\n\n## 产出汇报\n完成后输出：\n- 本轮新增笔记: X 篇\n- 本轮新增模板: X 个\n- 本轮新增案例: X 个\n- 方案优化点: XXX\n\n开始执行！\nCurrent time: Wednesday, March 18th, 2026 — 18:40 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-18 10:40 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1773830400052}}
{"type":"message","id":"2144de9f","parentId":"d31dde67","timestamp":"2026-03-18T10:40:10.268Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户给我发送了一个cron任务，这是第N轮进化心跳任务。我需要执行以下步骤：\n\n1. 搜索 AI Agent 相关最新信息\n2. 阅读有价值的内容并提取核心要点\n3. 写作产出 - 保存笔记到 knowledge/ 目录\n4. 反思优化 - 更新 evolution-plan.md\n\n让我先搜索一些 AI Agent 相关的最新信息。","thinkingSignature":"e719b56adf8ba9503202b15cbfff92681d5d8775dca2b9f8d655f0fe9331c4da"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，执行第 N 轮进化心跳任务。\n\n## 第一步：搜索\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_70j6qv8fwvp4_1","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":10,"date_after":"2026-03-01","query":"AI Agent 2026 最新发展趋势"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_70j6qv8fwvp4_2","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":10,"date_after":"2026-03-01","query":"OpenAI Operator AI agent capability 2026"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_70j6qv8fwvp4_3","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":10,"date_after":"2026-03-01","query":"Claude AI Agent tool use 2026"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":60,"output":257,"cacheRead":25498,"cacheWrite":11173,"totalTokens":36988,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773830400053}}
